name: Galactic Coordinates RA 111m | Dec +4° 4′ 4″
description:
Galactic Coordinates #4
The Blockchain Palace

In the vicinity of the Snake and Puma constellations floats the Blockchain palace, a structural tech maze of platforms resting on neo-corinthian columns. It surrounds the native AI who stands meditating, indifferent to the cosmic winds blowing through, and the Centaurian devs coding and marauding the overpasses, busy proliferating multiservice businesses.

Looking close it appears that one of the hosts is none other than the legendary @nftbiker as one cyborg skele Centaurian high operator with a motorbike body, running and continuously developing his tools for the people while collecting the finest gems of the market.
